<title>UK: UBS sets warrants on Ciba Speciality.</title>
<headline>UBS sets warrants on Ciba Speciality.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Union Bank of Switzerland said it has issued 20 million American-styel call warrants on registered shares of Ciba Speciality Chemicals.</p>
<p>One share is controlled by 10 warrants.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    160 CHF		   PREMIUM	22.6 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE     1.78 CHF		  GEARING	8.1 TIMES</p>
<p> EXERCISE PERIOD 02.JUN.97-15.JAN.99   PAYDATE	02.JUN.97</p>
<p> LISTING	   SWX			 MIN EXER LOT 100</p>
<p>SPOT REFERENCE  145 CHF</p>
<p>--Reuter London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
</text>
